6. Data Retention
We retain your information for as long as you use the App and as needed to provide the App's features. You may delete locally stored and synced app data using Delete All My Data in the App's Profile settings. Deletions intended to remove iCloud-synced records are propagated through your private iCloud container, subject to Apple's sync behavior and network availability.

Signing out of Sign in with Apple in the App clears your stored Apple identity in the App but does not by itself delete your drink logs or subscription.

7. Your Choices and Rights
Depending on your location, you may have rights to access, correct, delete, or restrict certain processing of your personal information.

Within the App, you can:

Decline or revoke HealthKit, camera, photo library, and notification permissions in iOS Settings

Sign out of Sign in with Apple in Profile

Delete All My Data in Profile to remove app data from your device and private iCloud sync where applicable

Manage or cancel subscriptions through your Apple ID subscription settings

To request assistance, contact us using the details in Section 12.

8. Children's Privacy
The App is not directed to children under 13 (or the minimum age required in your country). We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you believe a child has provided personal information through the App, please contact us so we can take appropriate steps.

9. Security
We use reasonable administrative, technical, and organizational measures designed to protect your information. No method of transmission or storage is completely secure. You are responsible for maintaining the security of your device and Apple ID.

10. International Users
If you use the App from outside the country where we operate, your information may be processed in countries where our service providers (including Apple, RevenueCat, and Google) maintain facilities. Those countries may have different data protection laws than your own.

11. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will revise the "Last updated" date at the top of this document when changes are posted. Continued use of the App after an update constitutes acceptance of the revised policy where permitted by law.

